   "duration":"10.00 min.",
   "text":"San Antonio UFO sighting in 1970 while parking with girlfriend. When I was about 16, my girl friend and I were parking, she said look at that light.  I said its just a plane.  Later, she said, look its moving around.  I said its just a hellicopter.  Then she said look its coming closer,then it dropped came up over the oak trees, about 100 feet away.  An oval yellowish white glow, humming.  Scared ((deleted)), I started truck, threw it in reverse and hauled ass.  Later, I realized the only way from such a far distance away it could have zoomed in on us had to be from my girlfriend looking and thinking about it, some sort of mental thalepophe. ((NUFORC Note:  Source of report indicates that the date of the sighting is approximate.  PD))",
