   "text":"(3) UFO's  viewed in Seminole, Oklahoma; above a little league baseball game. While Watching a baseball little league game, (3) oval shaped bright objects overflew the field at app. 2,500-3,000 ft in elevation, traveling from west to east, the speed of the over flight was extreme, thus lasting only a few moments, nevertheless, it got the attention of all who were watching the game, this including the players, as they paused to watch. This happened many years ago as I am now 60 years of age, aside from the people watching the game it was seen by my mother, (1) brother, (2) sisters, an aunt an (1) cousin,  Often revisited in conversation at family get togethers, even into this day.",
